  "title": "Locum Clinic Staff Nurse (Cannulation required! | IMMEDIATE START) #HJOT",
  "description": "<p><strong>We are hiring  Staff Nurses with IV Cannulation Skills to be outsourced to various healthcare institutions across Singapore!</strong><br>\n</p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Perform IV cannulation safely and efficiently</li>\n  <li>Administer medications and monitor patient responses</li>\n  <li>Provide nursing care in ward, clinic, or procedural settings</li>\n  <li>Assist in minor procedures and patient preparation</li>\n  <li>Maintain accurate documentation and uphold infection control standards</li>\n  <li>Communicate effectively with patients, families, and the healthcare team</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Valid SNB registration (EN/RN)</li>\n  <li>Competent in IV cannulation (with certification or proof of competency)</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently in fast-paced clinical environments</li>\n  <li>Prior experience in acute or outpatient settings preferred</li>\n  <li>Good interpersonal and communication skills</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>All interested candidates are invited to email your resume in MS Word format to:</p>\n<p><br>\n<strong>healthscience@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></p>\n<p>Please include your cannulation experience, full working history, notice period, and expected hourly rate.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Aaron Wong<br>\nHealthcare Outsourcing Team<br>\n<strong>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</strong><br>\nCompany Reg. No. 199601303W | EA License Number: 99C4599</p>\n<p><em>Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</em></p>",
